#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:37
msgid "Camera Navigation"
msgstr "Upravljanje kamerom"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:39
msgid ""
"There are several different ways to navigate and position the camera in "
"your scene, some of them are explained below."
msgstr ""
"Nudi vam se nekoliko načina za upravljanje i pozicioniranje kamere u "
"scene, neke od njih navodimo u daljem tekstu."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:41
msgid ""
"Zooming in and out is possible in this view, but to change the viewpoint,"
" you have to move or rotate the camera."
msgstr ""
"Zumiranje ka i od je dostupno u ovoj orijentaciji, ali pomeranje tačke "
"gledišta zahteva pomeranje ili rotaciju same kamere."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:46
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Remember that the active \"camera\" might be any kind of object. So these"
" actions can be used, for example, to position and aim a light."
msgstr ""
"Napominjemo da aktivna \"kamera\" može biti bilo koji objekat. Tako, ove "
"postupke možete koristi i za, npr. postavljanje i usmeravanje lampe."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:51
msgid "Move Active Camera to View"
msgstr "Move Active Camera to View"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:56
msgid "Object Mode"
msgstr "Object Mode"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:57
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl-Alt-Numpad0`"
msgstr ":kbd:`Ctrl-Alt-Numpad0`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:59
msgid ""
"This feature allows you to position and orient the active camera to match"
" your current viewport."
msgstr ""
"Ova funkcija pozicionira i orijentiše aktivnu kameru u skladu sa "
"trenutnim pravcem pogleda."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:61
msgid ""
"Select a camera and then move around in the 3D View to a desired position"
" and direction for your camera (so that you are seeing what you want the "
"camera to see). Now press :kbd:`Ctrl-Alt-Numpad0` and your selected "
"camera positions itself to match the view, and switches to camera view."
msgstr ""
"Markirajte (neku) kameru, a onda izvršite orijentaciju pogleda u 3D "
"prikazu onako kako želite (tako da vidite ono što želite i kamera da "
"vidi). Kada pritisnete :kbd:`Ctrl-Alt-Numpad0`, markirana kamera će se "
"poklopiti sa trenutnom orijentacijom, i prikaz će se promeniti na *pogled"
" kroz kameru*."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:68
msgid "Camera View Positioning"
msgstr "Camera View Positioning"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:70
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By enabling :ref:`Lock Camera to View <3dview-lock-camera-to-view>` in "
"the View panel of the Sidebar region, while in camera view, you can "
"navigate the 3D View as usual, while remaining in camera view. Controls "
"are exactly the same as when normally moving in 3D."
msgstr ""
"Dok gledate \"kroz kameru\", možete aktivirati opciju :ref:`Lock Camera "
"to View <3dview-lock-camera-to-view>` u panelu *View* u regiji "
"parametara. Ovim ćete naterati kameru da prati vaše kretanje kroz 3D "
"prostor, kao što ste to činili i bez kamere."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:76
msgid "Roll, Pan, Dolly, and Track"
msgstr "Roll, Pan, Dolly, and Track"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:78
msgid ""
"To perform these camera moves, the camera must first be *selected*, so "
"that it becomes the active object (while viewing through it, you can "
":kbd:`RMB` -- click on the solid rectangular edges to select it). The "
"following actions also assume that you are in camera view :kbd:`Numpad0`!"
" Having done so, you can now manipulate the camera using the same tools "
"that are used to manipulate any object:"
msgstr ""
"Da bi ste izvršili ove pokrete kamere, kamera mora da bude *markirana*, "
"tako da predstavlja aktivni objekat (ako već gledate kroz kameru, "
"pritisnite :kbd:`RMB` na punu liniju okvira kamere da bi ste je "
"markirali). Sledeći postupci pretpostavljaju da gledate kroz kameru, i "
"isti su kao i za svaki drugi objekat:"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:86
msgid "Roll"
msgstr "Roll"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:86
msgid ""
"Press :kbd:`R` to enter object rotation mode. The default will be to "
"rotate the camera in its local Z axis (the axis orthogonal to the camera "
"view), which is the definition of a camera \"roll\"."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite :kbd:`R` da bi ste započeli rotaciju. Podrazumevana osa "
"rotacije biće \"Z\" osa same kamere (osa koja prati pravac kamere), što "
"je i definicija termina \"roll\"."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:91
msgid "Vertical Pan or Pitch"
msgstr "Vertical Pan or Pitch"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:89
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This is just a rotation along the local X axis. Press :kbd:`R` to enter "
"object rotation mode, then :kbd:`X` twice (the first press selects the "
"*global* axis, pressing the same letter a second time selects the *local*"
" axis -- this works with any axis; see the :doc:`axis locking page "
"</scene_layout/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking>`)."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je isto što i rotacija po \"X\" osi objekta/kamere. Pritisnite "
":kbd:`R` da bi ste započeli rotaciju, zatim pritisnite :kbd:`X` dvaput "
"(prvi put birate *glavnu* osu, drugim pritiskom birate osu *objekta* -- "
"ovo važi za bilo koju osu; vidi :doc:`axis locking page "
"</editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/precision/axis_locking>`)."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:94
msgid "Horizontal Pan or Yaw"
msgstr "Horizontal Pan or Yaw"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:94
msgid ""
"This corresponds to a rotation around the camera's local Y axis. Press "
":kbd:`R`, and then :kbd:`Y` twice."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je isto što i rotacija oko \"Y\" ose kamere/objekta. Pritisnite "
":kbd:`R` a zatim dvaput :kbd:`Y`."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:96
msgid "Dolly"
msgstr "Dolly"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:97
msgid "To dolly the camera, press :kbd:`G` then :kbd:`MMB` (or :kbd:`Z` twice)."
msgstr ""
"Da \"prenesete\" kameru (\"dolly\"), pritisnite :kbd:`G` zatim :kbd:`MMB`"
" (ili :kbd:`Z` dvaput)."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:100
msgid "Sideways Tracking"
msgstr "Pomeranje u stranu"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:99
msgid ""
"Press :kbd:`G` and move the mouse (you can use :kbd:`X` twice or :kbd:`Y`"
" to get pure-horizontal or pure-vertical sideways tracking)."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite :kbd:`G` i pomerajte miša (koristite :kbd:`X` dvaput ili "
":kbd:`Y` da bi ograničili pokret na horizontalu ili vertikalu)."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:104
