msgid ":ref:`Fly/Walk Mode <3dview-fly-walk>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Fly/Walk Mode <3dview-walk-fly>`"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/navigate/camera_view.rst:105
msgid "When you are in walk/fly mode, navigation actually moves your camera."
msgstr ""
"Kada je aktivan specijalni režim \"walk/fly\", navigacijom vršite "
"translaciju kamere."

